commentable_entity.ask: We want JOHNNY DEPP back in 2021
commentable_entity.title: Johnny Depp: We want JOHNNY DEPP back in 2021
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp has been a phenomenal actor throughout his career. Depp was removed from the movie Pirates of the Caribbean by Walt Disney’s Company. This unfortunately is due to his ex wife Amber Heard lying and stating that Depp beat her. It has been proven that he did not hit her, but yet, that she beat on him repeatedly. She hit him with pots and pans 24/7 as if that was okay. This may come as a joke to some, but abuse towards a man or woman is not to be taken lightly. Now that this has come to light, Johnny Depp still has not been redeemed of this false news.

Amber Heard ruined Johnny Depp’s life as well as career. Johnny Depp has always been one of the greatest actors ever since he started acting around the age of 21. This man NEVER disappoints when he makes a movie, so why continue to keep him from doing Pirates of the Caribbean?? That movie is nothing without him! Please sign this petition to help Johnny Depp get back to what he enjoys and does best.

And Now in 2021, Amber Heard's lawyer has confirmed Amber did not donate her divorce settlement to charity and therefor lied to dying children and committed perjury in the UK

They have to bring him back to rule the seas again, UNLESS it is actor's own choice to withdraw from the role.

Even if it means nothing to you but please, sign this petition for the ones who REALLY want Johnny Depp

commentable_entity.petition_title: Johnny Depp: We want JOHNNY DEPP back in 2021

comment:
I will not support a self-confessed, yet unrepentant, abuser of at least two of her domestic partners. 
I’m signing because I’ve heard the tapes Ms Heard made in which she admits repeatedly hitting Mr. Depp, states she can’t promise not to again, clearly gaslights Mr. Depp, and engages in further violent & disgusting behaviors typical of some Cluster B personality disordered people- particularly Malignant Narcissism. In the tapes Mr. Depp can be heard endeavoring to navigate kindly in an impossible situation with someone behaving like a toxic malignant narcissist- classic conversation between abuser (Heard) & victim (Depp). Heard also has a verifiable legal history as a domestic abuser, which points to repetition compulsion.
Mr. Depp has surely lost too much already, let’s not continue to victimize and penalize him for the simple “crime” of falling for a girlmonster. Conversely let’s not reward Ms. Heard for her terrible behavior.
Both parties need help- Ms. Heard needs a 12 step & vitamin therapy for alcoholism, and Cognitive Behavioural Therapy; and Mr Depp needs trauma counseling, research on & therapy to heal his possible attachment disorder, & heal with holistic health therapies, along with Adeno B12 and top notch Genomic B-complex therapy. Both parties need to heal. And the world at large should Not be further abused by having to view films by, or be further gaslighted by, Heard.
commentable_entity.ask: We want JOHNNY DEPP back in 2021
commentable_entity.title: Johnny Depp: We want JOHNNY DEPP back in 2021
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp has been a phenomenal actor throughout his career. Depp was removed from the movie Pirates of the Caribbean by Walt Disney’s Company. This unfortunately is due to his ex wife Amber Heard lying and stating that Depp beat her. It has been proven that he did not hit her, but yet, that she beat on him repeatedly. She hit him with pots and pans 24/7 as if that was okay. This may come as a joke to some, but abuse towards a man or woman is not to be taken lightly. Now that this has come to light, Johnny Depp still has not been redeemed of this false news.

Amber Heard ruined Johnny Depp’s life as well as career. Johnny Depp has always been one of the greatest actors ever since he started acting around the age of 21. This man NEVER disappoints when he makes a movie, so why continue to keep him from doing Pirates of the Caribbean?? That movie is nothing without him! Please sign this petition to help Johnny Depp get back to what he enjoys and does best.

And Now in 2021, Amber Heard's lawyer has confirmed Amber did not donate her divorce settlement to charity and therefor lied to dying children and committed perjury in the UK

They have to bring him back to rule the seas again, UNLESS it is actor's own choice to withdraw from the role.

Even if it means nothing to you but please, sign this petition for the ones who REALLY want Johnny Depp

commentable_entity.title: Johnny Depp: We want JOHNNY DEPP back in 2021
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp has been a phenomenal actor throughout his career. Depp was removed from the movie Pirates of the Caribbean by Walt Disney’s Company. This unfortunately is due to his ex wife Amber Heard lying and stating that Depp beat her. It has been proven that he did not hit her, but yet, that she beat on him repeatedly. She hit him with pots and pans 24/7 as if that was okay. This may come as a joke to some, but abuse towards a man or woman is not to be taken lightly. Now that this has come to light, Johnny Depp still has not been redeemed of this false news.

Amber Heard ruined Johnny Depp’s life as well as career. Johnny Depp has always been one of the greatest actors ever since he started acting around the age of 21. This man NEVER disappoints when he makes a movie, so why continue to keep him from doing Pirates of the Caribbean?? That movie is nothing without him! Please sign this petition to help Johnny Depp get back to what he enjoys and does best.

And Now in 2021, Amber Heard's lawyer has confirmed Amber did not donate her divorce settlement to charity and therefor lied to dying children and committed perjury in the UK

They have to bring him back to rule the seas again, UNLESS it is actor's own choice to withdraw from the role.

Even if it means nothing to you but please, sign this petition for the ones who REALLY want Johnny Depp
